A. Blog Landing Page (/blog)
Hero Section: Latest post with large image.

Search Bar: Real-time or "on enter" search filtering posts by Title. (go with easiest approach)

Category Filter: Horizontal pill-buttons or dropdown to filter posts (e.g., "All", "Stories", "Tips").

Post Grid/List:

Cards displaying: Featured Image, Title, Category, Author Name, Publish Date, and Description snippet.

Pagination or "Load More" button (Limit 9-12 posts per view).

B. Single Blog Post Page (/blog/:slug)
Header: Title, Author (Avatar + Name), Publish Date, Category.

Featured Image: Large banner image.

Content Body: Renders rich text (HTML/Markdown) with proper styling for mobile readability.

Related Blogs:

Logic: Show 3 recent posts from the same category.

UI: Small grid at the bottom of the article.

3.2 Navigation Changes
Main Menu: Add "Blog" link to the header navigation.

Footer: Add "Blog" link to the site map.

All blog pages should be SEO optimised